    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Become the legendary Ninja Ball Warrior in ball-e!</h2>Master the art of parkour as you navigate through procedurally generated traps and obstacles. Upgrade your abilities to avoid falling and getting caught, or face restarting from the beginning.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/f2d2c2e726a01ed047bbba6c8500bf51.poster.avif?t=1726733141\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/f2d2c2e726a01ed047bbba6c8500bf51.webm?t=1726733141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/f2d2c2e726a01ed047bbba6c8500bf51.mp4?t=1726733141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Boss Battles!</h2>Defeat a variety of themed bosses to progress through the different stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/a36cf5276562d7070acc3287ac966a2a.avif?t=1726733141\" width=600 height=182 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Abilities, Upgrades, and Characters</h2>Discover and improve different abilities, upgrades, and characters with unique stats and starting abilities. <br>Unlock them by beating the different stages.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/dc73c2abf914eb64659f4f1e6c412a4f.poster.avif?t=1726733141\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/dc73c2abf914eb64659f4f1e6c412a4f.webm?t=1726733141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062990/extras/dc73c2abf914eb64659f4f1e6c412a4f.mp4?t=1726733141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Levels</h2>Enjoy endless challenges with procedurally generated levels that offer new obstacles every time.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fluid Physics-Based Movement</h2>Experience fluid and dynamic movement, allowing for various combinations of abilities. <br>Discover hidden tricks to become faster and more agile.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges and Training Mode</h2>Beat small challenges in the stadium and compete with friends on the leaderboard. <br>Hone your skills in training mode to become the Ultimate Ninja Ball Warrior.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ball-e is designed to be challenging. Check if this game is for you:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Love overcoming challenges<br></li><li> Enjoy improving skills and techniques<br></li><li> Learn from mistakes and do not give up easily<br></li><li> Enjoy challenging games like Getting Over It or Elden Ring<br></li><li> Like to show off beating difficult games<br></li><li> Love balls</li></ul>",
